title: Jiří Jeslínek (footballer, born 1987)
text:
Jiří Jeslínek (born 30 September 1987 in <a href="Prague">Prague</a>) is a Czech <a href="association%20football">football</a> who plays as a <a href="Striker%20%28association%20football%29">striker</a>.
Career.
In early 2011, Jeslínek signed a three-year contract with a <a href="Ukrainian%20Premier%20League">Ukrainian Premier League</a> side <a href="FC%20Kryvbas%20Kryvyi%20Rih">Kryvbas</a>.
In July 2013 Jeslínek returned to the <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a>, signing for <a href="FK%20Mlad%C3%A1%20Boleslav">Mladá Boleslav</a>, before moving to the <a href="Kazakhstan%20Premier%20League">Kazakhstan Premier League</a> in January 2014, signing for <a href="FC%20Tobol">FC Tobol</a>.
